<br>
my whole reasoning behind this is please don't take this as a flame but... well frankly spam is annoying, if you have ever played a melee you know that they get enough spam as it is they don't need more. i would also like to say it's not that hard to mash a 2nd key after you cast a spell, infact you get used to it rather quickly.<br>
